This was the error that was occurring 1 out of every 2-4
requests on an earlier test LOC crawl. My best guess was
that it was caused by http/1.1 kept-alive connections that
the other side was closing. (The comment near the HTTPClient
code that generates that error indicates the usual cause
is a closed connection.)

Our HTTP fetcher was changed to limit itself to http/1.0,
and I didn&#39;t see the errors on subsequent test crawls.

If it&#39;s returned, there must be another trigger of the
problem.

- Gordon


